{"title":"Potion of enlightenment/zh-CN","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Potion_of_enlightenment/zh-CN","type":"markdown","data":"**NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！**  \n[了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki](/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN \"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\")\n\n**[English](/wiki/Potion_of_enlightenment \"Potion of enlightenment\")** • [中文（中国大陆）‎]()\n\n| ! [![Pink potion.png](/images/7/79/Pink_potion.png)](/wiki/File:Pink_potion.png) |                                                                                                                  |\n| -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| 名称                                                                               | 启蒙                                                                                                               |\n| 外观                                                                               | [随机](/index.php?title=%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"随机外观 (page does not exist)\") |\n| 基础价                                                                              | 200 [zm](/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81 \"金币\")                                                                          |\n| 重量                                                                               | 20                                                                                                               |\n| 怪物使用                                                                             | *不会被怪物使用。*                                                                                                       |\n\n**启蒙药水**（potion of enlightenment）是[NetHack](/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")中的一种[药水](/wiki/%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4 \"药水\")。\n\n[ ]\n\n## Contents\n\n- [1 生成](#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90)\n\n- [2 描述](#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0)\n\n- [3 策略](#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5)\n\n- [4 历史](#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2)\n\n- [5 消息](#.E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF)\n\n- [6 Variants](#Variants)\n\n  - [6.1 UnNetHack](#UnNetHack)\n  - [6.2 Hack'EM](#Hack.27EM)\n\n- [7 引用及注释](#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A)\n\n## 生成\n\n启蒙药水在随机生成药水中占比2%。\n\n[巫师](/index.php?title=%E5%B7%AB%E5%B8%88\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"巫师 (page does not exist)\")在游戏开始时获得的随机药水中有可能出现启蒙药水。\n\n将[混乱药水](/wiki/%E6%B7%B7%E4%B9%B1%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4 \"混乱药水\")与[升级药水](/index.php?title=%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"升级药水 (page does not exist)\")或[获得能量药水](/wiki/%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4 \"获得能量药水\")[混合](/index.php?title=%E6%B5%B8\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"浸 (page does not exist)\")后有3⁄10的概率[调制](/index.php?title=%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"炼金术 (page does not exist)\")出启蒙药水。\n\n## 描述\n\n- *主条目：[启蒙](/index.php?title=%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"启蒙 (page does not exist)\")*\n\n[饮用](/index.php?title=%E9%A5%AE%E7%94%A8\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"饮用 (page does not exist)\")非诅咒的启蒙药水会[锻炼](/index.php?title=%E9%94%BB%E7%82%BC\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"锻炼 (page does not exist)\")玩家的[感知](/index.php?title=%E6%84%9F%E7%9F%A5\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"感知 (page does not exist)\")并提供一次[启蒙](/index.php?title=%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"启蒙 (page does not exist)\")，使得玩家能够了解自身当下拥有的[特质](/index.php?title=%E7%89%B9%E8%B4%A8\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"特质 (page does not exist)\")及其他属性[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1)。祝福的启蒙药水还会将玩家的[智力](/index.php?title=%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"智力 (page does not exist)\")和感知各提升1点[\\[2\\]](#cite_note-2)。\n\n饮用诅咒的启蒙药水会损害玩家的感知，输出一条消息，没有其他效果，若药水未鉴定，游戏会请求玩家对其进行类别[命名](/index.php?title=%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"命名 (page does not exist)\")[\\[3\\]](#cite_note-3)。\n\n将启蒙药水与[飘浮药水](/wiki/%E9%A3%98%E6%B5%AE%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4 \"飘浮药水\")混合有3⁄5的概率调制出[升级药水](/index.php?title=%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"升级药水 (page does not exist)\")。\n\n## 策略\n\n你可以考虑祝福启蒙药水来获取智力和感知加成，或是用于炼金术来制造升级药水。\n\n## 历史\n\n启蒙药水最初于[NetHack 3.0.0](/wiki/NetHack_3.0.0 \"NetHack 3.0.0\")加入游戏。\n\n## 消息\n\n- 你有一种不舒服的感觉……（You have an uneasy feeling...）\n\n  你喝下了一瓶被诅咒的启蒙药水。\n\n## Variants\n\n**此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。**  \n您可以帮助我们[**翻译此页面**](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Potion_of_enlightenment/zh-CN\\&action=edit)，但**请勿使用机器翻译**。\n\n### UnNetHack\n\nIn [UnNetHack](/wiki/UnNetHack \"UnNetHack\"), there is a 3⁄5 chance of a potion of enlightenment generating in the [boulder](/wiki/Boulder \"Boulder\")-blocked stash on the last floor of the [Dragon Caves](/wiki/Dragon_Caves \"Dragon Caves\") at level creation.\n\n### Hack'EM\n\nIn [Hack'EM](/wiki/Hack%27EM \"Hack'EM\"), the last floor of [The Wyrm Caves](/wiki/The_Wyrm_Caves \"The Wyrm Caves\") uses the last floor map from the Dragon Caves of UnNetHack, including the 3⁄5 chance of generating a potion of enlightenment in the stash.\n\n## 引用及注释\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 713](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L713)\n2. [↑](#cite_ref-2) [src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 719](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L719)\n3. [↑](#cite_ref-3) [src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 716](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L716)\n\n[![此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。](/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png)](/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version \"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\")\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Potion of enlightenment/zh-CN - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.