tion of enlightenment/zh-CN</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"><span class=\"subpages\">&lt; <a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_enlightenment\" title=\"Potion of enlightenment\">Potion of enlightenment</a></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"width:50%;margin:auto;border:solid 3px #32CD32;background-color:#00FF00;text-align:center;clear:both\">\n<p><b>NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！</b><br />\n<a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN\" title=\"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\">了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki</a>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"languages\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/Potion_of_enlightenment\" title=\"Potion of enlightenment\">English</a></b>\n<p><span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n&#160;&#8226;&#32;<span lang=\"zh-CN\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">中文（中国大陆）‎</a></span></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-brightmagenta\">!</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Pink_potion.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Pink potion.png\" src=\"/images/7/79/Pink_potion.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>启蒙\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>外观\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"随机外观 (page does not exist)\">随机</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>200 <a href=\"/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"金币\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td>20\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>怪物使用\n</th>\n<td><small><i>不会被怪物使用。</i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>启蒙药水</b>（potion of enlightenment）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"药水\">药水</a>。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">描述</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#.E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">消息</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#UnNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">UnNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Hack.27EM\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Hack'EM</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p>启蒙药水在随机生成药水中占比2%。\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B7%AB%E5%B8%88&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"巫师 (page does not exist)\">巫师</a>在游戏开始时获得的随机药水中有可能出现启蒙药水。\n</p><p>将<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%B7%B7%E4%B9%B1%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"混乱药水\">混乱药水</a>与<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"升级药水 (page does not exist)\">升级药水</a>或<a href=\"/wiki/%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"获得能量药水\">获得能量药水</a><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%B5%B8&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"浸 (page does not exist)\">混合</a>后有<sup>3</sup>&#8260;<sub>10</sub>的概率<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"炼金术 (page does not exist)\">调制</a>出启蒙药水。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"描述\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\">描述</span></h2>\n<dl><dd><div class=\"noprint relarticle mainarticle\"><i>主条目：<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"启蒙 (page does not exist)\">启蒙</a></i></div></dd></dl>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A5%AE%E7%94%A8&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"饮用 (page does not exist)\">饮用</a>非诅咒的启蒙药水会<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%94%BB%E7%82%BC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"锻炼 (page does not exist)\">锻炼</a>玩家的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%84%9F%E7%9F%A5&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"感知 (page does not exist)\">感知</a>并提供一次<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"启蒙 (page does not exist)\">启蒙</a>，使得玩家能够了解自身当下拥有的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%89%B9%E8%B4%A8&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"特质 (page does not exist)\">特质</a>及其他属性<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。祝福的启蒙药水还会将玩家的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"智力 (page does not exist)\">智力</a>和感知各提升1点<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p><p>饮用诅咒的启蒙药水会损害玩家的感知，输出一条消息，没有其他效果，若药水未鉴定，游戏会请求玩家对其进行类别<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%91%BD%E5%90%8D&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"命名 (page does not exist)\">命名</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p><p>将启蒙药水与<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%A3%98%E6%B5%AE%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"飘浮药水\">飘浮药水</a>混合有<sup>3</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub>的概率调制出<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"升级药水 (page does not exist)\">升级药水</a>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>你可以考虑祝福启蒙药水来获取智力和感知加成，或是用于炼金术来制造升级药水。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>启蒙药水最初于<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_3.0.0\" title=\"NetHack 3.0.0\">NetHack 3.0.0</a>加入游戏。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"消息\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF\">消息</span></h2>\n<dl><dt><span id=\".E4.BD.A0.E6.9C.89.E4.B8.80.E7.A7.8D.E4.B8.8D.E8.88.92.E6.9C.8D.E7.9A.84.E6.84.9F.E8.A7.89.E2.80.A6.E2.80.A6\">你有一种不舒服的感觉……</span>（You have an uneasy feeling...）</dt>\n<dd>你喝下了一瓶被诅咒的启蒙药水。</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Potion_of_enlightenment/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"UnNetHack\">UnNetHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/UnNetHack\" title=\"UnNetHack\">UnNetHack</a>, there is a <sup>3</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub> chance of a potion of enlightenment generating in the <a href=\"/wiki/Boulder\" title=\"Boulder\">boulder</a>-blocked stash on the last floor of the <a href=\"/wiki/Dragon_Caves\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragon Caves\">Dragon Caves</a> at level creation.\n</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Hack'EM\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hack.27EM\">Hack'EM</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/Hack%27EM\" title=\"Hack&#39;EM\">Hack'EM</a>, the last floor of <a href=\"/wiki/The_Wyrm_Caves\" title=\"The Wyrm Caves\">The Wyrm Caves</a> uses the last floor map from the Dragon Caves of UnNetHack, including the <sup>3</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub> chance of generating a potion of enlightenment in the stash.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L713\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 713</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L719\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 719</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L716\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 716</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926185732\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.037 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.052 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 594/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 3050/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5821/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 855/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1198/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   38.100      1 -total\n 20.36%    7.756      1 Template:Languages\n 18.60%    7.087      3 Template:Refsrc\n 15.48%    5.898      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\n 15.22%    5.799      5 Template:Languages/Lang\n 12.41%    4.728      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\n  9.67%    3.683      1 Template:Potion/zh-CN\n  8.74%    3.329      1 Template:Message/zh-CN\n  7.69%    2.930      3 Template:Refsrc/link\n  6.33%    2.410      1 Template:Main/zh-CN\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:41031-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926185732 and revision id 177021\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Potion_of_enlightenment/zh-CN&amp;oldid=177021\">https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Potion_of_enlightenment/zh-CN&amp;oldid=177021</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a href=\"/wiki/Special:Categories\" title=\"Special:Categories\">Categories</a>: <ul><li><a hre