:{\"value\":4,\"limit\":100},\"unstrip-depth\":{\"value\":0,\"limit\":20},\"unstrip-size\":{\"value\":1198,\"limit\":5000000},\"timingprofile\":[\"100.00%   38.100      1 -total\",\" 20.36%    7.756      1 Template:Languages\",\" 18.60%    7.087      3 Template:Refsrc\",\" 15.48%    5.898      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\",\" 15.22%    5.799      5 Template:Languages/Lang\",\" 12.41%    4.728      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\",\"  9.67%    3.683      1 Template:Potion/zh-CN\",\"  8.74%    3.329      1 Template:Message/zh-CN\",\"  7.69%    2.930      3 Template:Refsrc/link\",\"  6.33%    2.410      1 Template:Main/zh-CN\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240926185732\",\"ttl\":604800,\"transientcontent\":false}}});mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":101});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{needhelp/zh-CN}}\n{{languages}}\n{{potion/zh-CN|name=启蒙|cost=200}}\n'''启蒙药水'''（potion of enlightenment）是{{cnlink|NetHack}}中的一种[[药水]]。\n\n== 生成 ==\n启蒙药水在随机生成药水中占比2%。\n\n[[巫师]]在游戏开始时获得的随机药水中有可能出现启蒙药水。\n\n将[[混乱药水]]与[[升级药水]]或[[获得能量药水]][[浸|混合]]后有{{frac|3|10}}的概率[[炼金术|调制]]出启蒙药水。\n\n== 描述 ==\n{{main/zh-CN|启蒙}}\n[[饮用]]非诅咒的启蒙药水会[[锻炼]]玩家的[[感知]]并提供一次[[启蒙]]，使得玩家能够了解自身当下拥有的[[特质]]及其他属性{{refsrc|src/potion.c|713|nethack=3.6.7}}。祝福的启蒙药水还会将玩家的[[智力]]和感知各提升1点{{refsrc|src/potion.c|719|nethack=3.6.7}}。\n\n饮用诅咒的启蒙药水会损害玩家的感知，输出一条消息，没有其他效果，若药水未鉴定，游戏会请求玩家对其进行类别[[命名]]{{refsrc|src/potion.c|716|nethack=3.6.7}}。\n\n将启蒙药水与[[飘浮药水]]混合有{{frac|3|5}}的概率调制出[[升级药水]]。\n\n== 策略 ==\n你可以考虑祝福启蒙药水来获取智力和感知加成，或是用于炼金术来制造升级药水。\n\n== 历史 ==\n启蒙药水最初于[[NetHack 3.0.0]]加入游戏。\n\n== 消息 ==\n{{message/zh-CN|你有一种不舒服的感觉……|你喝下了一瓶被诅咒的启蒙药水。|You have an uneasy feeling...}}\n\n==Variants==\n{{translation/zh-CN|n}}\n===UnNetHack===\nIn [[UnNetHack]], there is a {{frac|3|5}} chance of a potion of enlightenment generating in the [[boulder]]-blocked stash on the last floor of the [[Dragon Caves]] at level creation.\n\n===Hack'EM===\nIn [[Hack'EM]], the last floor of [[The Wyrm Caves]] uses the last floor map from the Dragon Caves of UnNetHack, including the {{frac|3|5}} chance of generating a potion of enlightenment in the stash.\n\n== 引用及注释 ==\n<references/>\n{{nethack-367/zh-CN}}\n[[Category:Potions/zh-CN|QIMENG]]"}